EO3真我杯主题赛——文案pm"></a><strong>2022.04</strong>             <strong>realme GT NEO3真我杯主题赛——文案pm</strong></h4><ul><li>结合品牌产品及电竞赛事，以具有噱头的总裁下场为起点，联动众多明星电竞kol参与比赛，打造热点事件。作为文案负责人，进行创意设想、活动策划撰写、宣传文案撰写及赛事直播流程/建议撰写工作。 </li></ul><!-- 图片资源 --><blockquote><p><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-55.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-56.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-57.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-58.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-59.png"></p></blockquote><h4 id="2022-05-娱非凡武汉店开业——项目pm"><a href="#2022-05-娱非凡武汉店开业——项目pm" class="headerlink" title="2022.05             娱非凡武汉店开业——项目pm"></a><strong>2022.05</strong>             <strong>娱非凡武汉店开业——项目pm</strong></h4><ul><li>根据潮玩店特性，联动电竞及本地/大众媒体资源，打造娱非凡首店开业营销事件。作为项目负责人，进行活动策划撰写、对接自有电竞资源、宣传文案和素材整理工作。微博总曝光超过<span style="color:#C00000;font-size:20px;"><strong>9784w</strong></span>，总阅读量超过<span style="color:#C00000;font-size:20px;"><strong>1.3亿</strong></span>。</li></ul><!-- 图片资源 --><blockquote><p><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-60.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-61.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-62.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-63.png"><br><span style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold"><a href="http://weibo.com/3293742405/LqGMappl25pxV">↓↓↓点我跳转↓↓↓</a></span><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-64.png"><br><span style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold"><a href="https://weibo.com/1162906045/LqGUiejic">↓↓↓点我跳转↓↓↓</a></span><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-65.png"><br><span style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold"><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/zcEXHyKz1s5lErJQPqZ2Aw">↓↓↓点我跳转↓↓↓</a></span><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-66.png"><br><span style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold"><a href="https://v.douyin.com/FD3uQoP/">↓↓↓点我跳转↓↓↓</a></span><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-67.png"></p></blockquote><h4 id="2022-08-京东游戏电视营销方案——文案pm"><a href="#2022-08-京东游戏电视营销方案——文案pm" class="headerlink" title="2022.08             京东游戏电视营销方案——文案pm"></a><strong>2022.08</strong>             <strong>京东游戏电视营销方案——文案pm</strong></h4><ul><li>结合产品特点，联动S12总决赛、线上会场搭建、明星kol选手资源、线下限定物料及联动品牌互换电竞资源方式，打造以电竞+产品为核心的综合化营销事件。作为文案负责人，进行创意构思、策划活动撰写及宣传工作。</li></ul><!-- 图片资源 --><blockquote><p><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-68.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-69.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-70.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-71.png"></p></blockquote><h4 id="2022-09-京东电器浪里个浪校园开学盛典——项目pm"><a href="#2022-09-京东电器浪里个浪校园开学盛典——项目pm" class="headerlink" title="2022.09             京东电器浪里个浪校园开学盛典——项目pm"></a><strong>2022.09</strong>             <strong>京东电器浪里个浪校园开学盛典——项目pm</strong></h4><ul><li>以学生为核心，联合12+KA品牌、多所头部院校、京东超体资源，为学生提供专属品牌福利及独特的1+3成长模式。作为项目负责人，进行开学盛典及造浪团创意构思、策划活动撰写及宣传工作。盛典直播观看<span style="color:#C00000;font-size:20px;"><strong>30w</strong></span>，视频号/公众号涨粉<span style="color:#C00000;font-size:20px;"><strong>3w</strong></span>，小程序单日PV<span style="color:#C00000;font-size:20px;"><strong>60w</strong></span>，UV<span style="color:#C00000;font-size:20px;"><strong>6w</strong></span>。</li></ul><!-- 图片资源 --><blockquote><p><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-73.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-75.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-76.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-78.png"><br><span style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold"><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/status/4815729319480822?wm=3333_2001&amp;from=10C9193010&amp;sourcetype=weixin">↓↓↓点我跳转↓↓↓</a></span><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-79.png"><br><span style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold"><a href="https://weibo.com/6428038435/M62sJrEQ3?refer_flag=1001030103_">↓↓↓点我跳转↓↓↓</a></span><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-80.png"><br><span style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold">[↓↓↓开学盛典现场返图↓↓↓]</span><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061315543.jpg"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061320203.jpg"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061320960.jpg"></p></blockquote><h4 id="2022-10-石家庄京东超体MALL开业营销方案——项目pm"><a href="#2022-10-石家庄京东超体MALL开业营销方案——项目pm" class="headerlink" title="2022.10             石家庄京东超体MALL开业营销方案——项目pm"></a><strong>2022.10</strong>             <strong>石家庄京东超体MALL开业营销方案——项目pm</strong></h4><ul><li>以石家庄电竞环境、京东MALL开业及英雄联盟S12赛事节点为核心，打造集潮玩娱乐、电竞赛事、舞台表演、特色场地搭建、动线直播互动的综合化开业营销活动。作为项目负责人，主导并参与京东MALL开业创意构思、策划撰写及宣传工作。动线活动参与人次<span style="color:#C00000;font-size:20px;"><strong>1.8w</strong></span>，现场参与水友赛及互动人次<span style="color:#C00000;font-size:20px;"><strong>7500+</strong></span>，抖音直播观看<span style="color:#C00000;font-size:20px;"><strong>5.9w</strong></span>。</li></ul><!-- 图片资源 --><blockquote><p><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-81.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-82.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-83.png"><br><span style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold"><a href="https://weibo.com/1558597584/McgmwgxIn?pagetype=profilefeed">↓↓↓点我跳转↓↓↓</a></span><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-86.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-77.png"><br><span style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold">[↓↓↓石家庄京东MALL开业现场返图↓↓↓]</span><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061325274.JPG"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061325081.JPG"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061327048.JPG"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061329337.JPG"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061406621.JPG"></p></blockquote><h4 id="2022-10-S12快闪区域线下传播方案——文案pm"><a href="#2022-10-S12快闪区域线下传播方案——文案pm" class="headerlink" title="2022.10             S12快闪区域线下传播方案——文案pm"></a><strong>2022.10</strong>             <strong>S12快闪区域线下传播方案——文案pm</strong></h4><ul><li>以沈阳、西安京东MALL、重庆、合肥京东超体为线下场景，结合时下最热S12赛事，为电竞玩家打造室内+户外S12京东电竞线下狂欢，并基于各地特色打造不同趣味话题，提升本地居民认知度。作为文案负责人，进行西安站分项的创意构思、策划活动撰写及宣传工作。</li></ul><!-- 图片资源 --><blockquote><p><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061407629.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061407546.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061407007.png"></p></blockquote><h4 id="2022-10-S12-OATLY联名观赛活动——项目pm"><a href="#2022-10-S12-OATLY联名观赛活动——项目pm" class="headerlink" title="2022.10             S12 OATLY联名观赛活动——项目pm"></a><strong>2022.10</strong>             <strong>S12 OATLY联名观赛活动——项目pm</strong></h4><ul><li>石家庄、沈阳京东MALL、重庆、合肥超体线下观赛活动为支点，联动知名燕麦奶品牌OATLY作为京东电竞应援早餐，解决用户早起观赛刚需。作为项目负责人，主导并参与OATLY联名应援早餐、手提袋、mini杯及杯套设计。四城快闪总人流量达<span style="color:#C00000;font-size:20px;"><strong>29.2w</strong></span>，凌晨观赛人数超<span style="color:#C00000;font-size:20px;"><strong>300</strong></span>人次，周边礼品发送数达<span style="color:#C00000;font-size:20px;"><strong>4000+</strong></span>。</li></ul><!-- 图片资源 --><blockquote><p><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061410446.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061410174.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061410273.png"><br><span style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold"> [↓↓↓OATLY联名店现场返图↓↓↓]</span><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061410312.JPG"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061411680.JPG"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061412102.JPG"><br><span style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold"> [↓↓↓OATLY联名限定周边返图↓↓↓]</span><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061412041.jpg"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061415540.jpg"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061416003.jpg"></p></blockquote><h4 id="2022-11-京东美妆跨年传播规划——文案pm"><a href="#2022-11-京东美妆跨年传播规划——文案pm" class="headerlink" title="2022.11             京东美妆跨年传播规划——文案pm"></a><strong>2022.11</strong>             <strong>京东美妆跨年传播规划——文案pm</strong></h4><ul><li>    以新为跨年传播关键词，提出新场景、新需求、新人群概念，跨界联动JDG战队，向核心电竞用户传递京东美妆品牌心智，打造京东美妆xJDG新年见面会标杆事件，以JDG战队为载体，搭建品牌与用户沟通桥梁。作为文案负责人，进行项目各阶段的创意构思、策划活动撰写及宣传工作。</li></ul><!-- 图片资源 --><blockquote><p><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061424042.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061424307.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061424412.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061424898.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061424811.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/202212061424586.png"></p></blockquote></span></span>]]></content>
      
      
