font-size:20px;"><strong>20w</strong></span>，本地校园kol曝光量超过<span style="color:#0070C0;font-size:20px;"><strong>50w</strong></span>。</p></li></ul><!-- 图片资源 --><blockquote><p><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-15.png"><br><span style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold"> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/2988492811/4696318431724087">↓↓↓点我跳转↓↓↓</a></span><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-16.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-17.png"><br><span style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold"> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/5765298156/4696319131915171">↓↓↓点我跳转↓↓↓</a></span><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-18.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-19.png"></p></blockquote><h4 id="2021-10-王者荣耀高校行西安美院站——文案pm"><a href="#2021-10-王者荣耀高校行西安美院站——文案pm" class="headerlink" title="2021.10             王者荣耀高校行西安美院站——文案pm"></a><strong>2021.10</strong>             <strong>王者荣耀高校行西安美院站——文案pm</strong></h4><p><span style="color:#0070C0;font-size:24px;"><strong>[腾讯西北片区王者荣耀优秀&amp;创新&amp;重要业务获奖项目]</strong></span></p><ul><li>联动西安美术学院双创艺术节，打造光影主题王者荣耀高校行，协同策划艺术展。作为文案负责人进行活动流程设计、宣传及素材整理工作。前宣视频登上王者荣耀官方视频号，传播量超过<span style="color:#0070C0;font-size:20px;"><strong>2000w</strong></span>。  </li></ul><!-- 图片资源 --><blockquote><p><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-01.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-02.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-03.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-04.png"><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-05.png"><br><span style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold"> <a href="https://b23.tv/WzqwWa">↓↓↓点我跳转↓↓↓</a></span><br><img src="https://bobofish.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/img/t-06.png"><br><span style="font-size:25px;font-weight:bold"> <a href="https://b23.tv/DhjATY">↓↓↓点我跳转↓↓↓</a></span><br><